<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 15:14:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>立法者希望美国解决中国农业无人机带来的风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/lawmakers-want-us-address-risks-posed-by-chinese-agriculture-drones-2024-09-06/</link><description>周五，十几名美国议员敦促拜登政府解决中国制造的农业无人机的使用问题，称这些无人机在美国农场的使用构成国家安全风险。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 14:14:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/lawmakers-want-us-address-risks-posed-by-chinese-agriculture-drones-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>随着电动汽车需求放缓，汽车制造商调整电气化计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/carmakers-adjust-electrification-plans-ev-demand-slows-2024-09-06/</link><description>据报道，日本丰田汽车已将 2026 年电动汽车生产计划削减三分之一，成为最新一家因需求放缓而缩减电动汽车计划的汽车制造商。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 12:12:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/carmakers-adjust-electrification-plans-ev-demand-slows-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>三十年后中国停止外国收养儿童</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-stops-foreign-adoptions-its-children-after-three-decades-2024-09-06/</link><description>政府表示，中国将不再将儿童送往海外收养，这推翻了源于其曾经严格的独生子女政策的长达三十多年的规定。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 09:50:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-stops-foreign-adoptions-its-children-after-three-decades-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>美国特使表示，中美在本周的会谈中“缩小”了气候融资方面的分歧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/us-china-still-have-some-differences-climate-finance-us-envoy-says-2024-09-06/</link><description>美国气候特使约翰·波德斯塔周五在北京表示，中美在气候融资等问题上仍存在“一些分歧”，但在本周的会谈中在缩小分歧方面取得了进展。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 09:32:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/us-china-still-have-some-differences-climate-finance-us-envoy-says-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国请求世贸组织与加拿大就关税问题进行磋商</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-it-submits-request-canada-wto-consultation-over-tariffs-2024-09-06/</link><description>中国周五表示，已要求在世界贸易组织与加拿大就渥太华对其电动汽车以及钢铁和铝制品征收的关税进行谈判，同一周北京宣布计划对加拿大油菜籽进口进行调查。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 09:27:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-it-submits-request-canada-wto-consultation-over-tariffs-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>北约秘书长敦促中国停止支持俄罗斯乌克兰战争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/nato-chief-urges-china-stop-supporting-russias-war-ukraine-2024-09-06/</link><description>他说，北京的帮助是战争继续下去的一个重要因素。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 08:56:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/nato-chief-urges-china-stop-supporting-russias-war-ukraine-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>Jean Paul Gaultier 所有者 Puig 报告称，IPO 成本导致利润下降 26%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/beauty-company-puigs-half-year-profit-drops-26-following-ipo-2024-09-06/</link><description>奢华美容和时尚公司 Puig 周五公布，其作为上市公司首次公布的盈利大幅下降，原因是其今年早些时候首次公开募股 (IPO) 相关的成本，导致其股价下跌多达 13%。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 07:53:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/beauty-company-puigs-half-year-profit-drops-26-following-ipo-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>韩国芯片高管因涉嫌向中国泄露技术而再次被捕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/south-korean-chip-executive-detained-again-over-alleged-technology-leak-china-2024-09-06/</link><description>一名法院官员及其律师周五表示，一名被指控窃取三星电子开发的半导体信息的韩国高管因与盗窃芯片处理技术有关的新指控而再次被拘留。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 04:26:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/south-korean-chip-executive-detained-again-over-alleged-technology-leak-china-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>超强台风八木袭击中国海南，扰乱数百万人的生活</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/super-typhoon-yagi-slams-southern-china-shutting-schools-cancelling-flights-2024-09-06/</link><description>今年亚洲最强台风“八木”周五登陆中国海南，带来狂风大雨，引发大面积停电，使素有“中国夏威夷”之称的旅游岛省陷入瘫痪。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 00:38:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/super-typhoon-yagi-slams-southern-china-shutting-schools-cancelling-flights-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>美国和中国指挥官将在“未来几周”讨论预防冲突</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-china-commanders-discuss-conflict-prevention-in-next-few-weeks-2024-09-05/</link><description>美国驻华大使周四表示，驻印太美军司令将在未来几周内与中国武装部队南部战区司令进行通话，目的是防止超级大国之间出现任何军事误解。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 19:41:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-china-commanders-discuss-conflict-prevention-in-next-few-weeks-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>南非总统称中国不会将非洲推入债务陷阱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/china-is-not-pushing-africa-into-debt-trap-south-african-president-says-2024-09-05/</link><description>南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨周四表示，他不认为中国在非洲的投资会将非洲大陆推入“债务陷阱”，而是互利关系的一部分。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 14:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/china-is-not-pushing-africa-into-debt-trap-south-african-president-says-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>摩根大通以“关税战2.0”风险为由放弃购买中国股票的呼吁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/jpmorgan-ditches-call-buy-chinese-stocks-citing-tariff-war-20-risk-2024-09-05/</link><description>摩根大通放弃了对中国股票的买入建议，警告 11 月美国大选后可能出现第二次关税战的风险，并对中国经济增长表示担忧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 08:53:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/jpmorgan-ditches-call-buy-chinese-stocks-citing-tariff-war-20-risk-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚和日本批评中国对菲律宾的“危险”行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-japan-criticise-china-dangerous-acts-towards-philippines-2024-09-05/</link><description>澳大利亚和日本周四批评中国在南海对菲律宾采取“危险和胁迫”行为。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 08:17:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-japan-criticise-china-dangerous-acts-towards-philippines-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促美国“立即”取消对中国商品的所有关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-urges-us-immediately-lift-all-tariffs-chinese-goods-2024-09-05/</link><description>中国商务部周四表示，在拜登政府宣布预计对包括电动汽车在内的中国制造的商品加征关税之前，美国应立即取消对中国商品的所有关税。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 07:53:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-urges-us-immediately-lift-all-tariffs-chinese-goods-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，中国因数据、药品进口调查而拘留了阿斯利康员工</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/china-detains-astrazeneca-staff-data-drug-import-probes-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-05/</link><description>据彭博社周四援引知情人士的话报道，中国警方拘留了阿斯利康的五名现任和前任员工，对他们可能从事的非法活动进行询问。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 07:25:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/china-detains-astrazeneca-staff-data-drug-import-probes-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>